                        "displayName": "Bart Blaszczyk",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It seems that the translator is not set when Zend_Form_Element_File is rendered separately.\r\nIf I set the translator explicitely (Zend_Form_Element_File::setTranslator()) in the controller before rendering the form, then translation works fine.",
