                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "There is no translator set... wether in the form nor within the element.\r\nSo how should translation work without a translation instance?\r\n\r\nI expect missing informations...",
